<p>He canceled the visit and blamed rain for the decision, saying the helicopter couldn’t fly and Secret Service couldn’t drive him there.</p>

<p>In a separate conversation on the same trip, Trump referred to more than 1,800 marines who died at Belleau Wood as 'suckers' for getting killed.</p>

<p>Trump denied ever saying those statements. </p>

<p>On Friday Trump said that his former chief of staff John Kelly 'could have been' a source for those claims.</p>

<p>Four people with alleged knowledge of the cemetery incident claimed it happened, to the magazine.</p>

<p>Trump has been heavily criticized for the shocking comments that disrespect veterans and war heroes.</p>

<p>Former secretary of defense Chuck Hagel, a Republican, said the remarks are 'credible' due to Trump’s track record of denigrating military personnel.</p>

<p>He’s made audacious comments against former US defense secretary James Mattis and US Senator John McCain. </p>
